**Impact: Small but enables future optimizations**
**Files to modify: `cache.go`**

### What to do

Add Width and Height fields to `CachedEntry`. This enables Optimization #4
(aspect-ratio pre-grouping) to work **without any file I/O on rescans**.

### Implementation

```go
